sources.description:
Deadlier than the teeth of the tiger shark!
A mutated giant octopus wreaks havoc on a California seaside community.

Original title: Tentacoli (1977) 

This film is available with subtitles in many language options.

Director: Ovidio G. Assonitis
Writers: Jerome Max, Tito Carpi, Steven W. Carabatsos
Stars: John Huston, Shelley Winters, Bo Hopkins, Henry Fonda
Genres: Action, Adventure, Comedy, Horror, Sci-Fi, Thriller
Budget: $5,000,000 (estimated)
